    {
      "id": "2018-r2-phys-9",
      "number": "II-C 问3",
      "topic": "p-V 图像中的吸热量",
      "topicTag": "热力学·热力学第一定律",
      "questionType": "choice",
      "humanVerified": true,
      "answer_match": true,
      "needs_review": false,
      "japanese": "一定量单原子理想气体按 $p-V$ 图从状态 A 经 B 到 C。A 为 $(V_0,p_0)$，B 为 $(2V_0,p_0)$，C 为 $(3V_0,p_0/2)$。求全过程气体吸收的热量。",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "①",
          "content": "$\\dfrac12p_0V_0$"
        },
        {
          "label": "②",
          "content": "$p_0V_0$"
        },
        {
          "label": "③",
          "content": "$\\dfrac32p_0V_0$"
        },
        {
          "label": "④",
          "content": "$2p_0V_0$"
        },
        {
          "label": "⑤",
          "content": "$\\dfrac52p_0V_0$"
        }
      ],
      "questionImage": "/images/2018_R2_physics/q09.png",
      "solution": {
        "translation": "用热力学第一定律 $Q=\\Delta U+W$。单原子理想气体内能 $U=\\frac32pV$。",
        "analysis": "A 到 C 的 $pV$ 从 $p_0V_0$ 变为 $\\frac12p_0\\cdot3V_0=\\frac32p_0V_0$。",
        "steps": [
          {
            "title": "(1) 内能变化",
            "content": "$$\\Delta U=\\frac32\\left(\\frac32p_0V_0-p_0V_0\\right)=\\frac34p_0V_0$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(2) 气体做功",
            "content": "A 到 B：$$W_{AB}=p_0V_0$$\n\nB 到 C 为梯形面积：$$W_{BC}=\\frac{p_0+p_0/2}{2}V_0=\\frac34p_0V_0$$\n\n$$W=\\frac74p_0V_0$$"
          },
          {
            "title": "(3) 求吸热量",
            "content": "$$Q=\\Delta U+W=\\frac34p_0V_0+\\frac74p_0V_0=\\frac52p_0V_0$$"
          }
        ],
        "finalAnswer": "⑤ $\\dfrac52p_0V_0$",
        "correctOption": "⑤"
      }
    },
